nt.com\nDonations appreciated (to help pay for hosting and related expenses). Please help:   \nhttps://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick\u0026hosted_button_id=64QMBRBXQSV6G\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/bookstore.htm\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see: https://www.youtube.com/billvicars\nTo learn basic fingerspelling see https://youtu.be/va1aAXpVr2w\n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages-layout/instructor.htm\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\n- Dr. Bill\n:)","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MvtVsr3P098/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCKgBEF5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLDSJE_pHFeJ6UKAKtwSL7p4nSfSug","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MvtVsr3P098/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCMQBEG5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLD2YTc5-qCAxG4TwI7wOgbuY5X_0Q","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MvtVsr3P098/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCPYBEIoBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLBoZ6nn-cVeDsA-Oltd92nEhE1RCg","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MvtVsr3P098/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCNACELwBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLBvrltNRHDDe0EPQmX8lZ3mX8Tonw","width":336,"height":188}]},"allowRatings":true,"viewCount":"2294","author":"Signs","isPrivate":false,"isUnpluggedCorpus":false,"isLiveContent":false,"isTvfilmVideo":false},"playerConfig":{"granularVariableSpeedConfig":{"minimumPlaybackRate":25,"maximumPlaybackRate":200,"stepSize":5,"defaultPlaybackRateOptions":[{"label":"1.0","value":100,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":5},{"label":"1.25","value":125,"isPremiumUpsell":false,"priority":2},{"label":"1.5","value":150,"isPremiumUps